# Agri-Surplus Trader Portal (LogiTech)
### Build2Break Hackathon - Team [Your Team Name]

## ðŸ“Œ Problem Statement
Farmers often struggle to find immediate storage for surplus produce. This portal allows **Traders** to digitize collected crops and **automatically allocates** the nearest available warehouse based on real-time capacity, ensuring zero food wastage.

